data.description: CUSTON BUILT FULL BRICK HOME ON ONE ACRE LOT. Open floor plan and towering ceilings. The foyer welcomes you to the Dining Room, Great Room, Gourmet Kitchen with dining area, and Family Room.  Isolate Master Suite on Level 1 with 3 additional bedrooms and a bonus room upstairs. Beautiful staircase that overlooks the foyer and Great Room.  Two Fireplaces, Crown molding throughout, vaulted, coffered, and trey ceilings.  Plenty of unfinished attic space for storage.  MOVE IN READY! SEE IT TODAY!
